ggplot(data, aes(x = kozak_region,
                 y = mean_ratio)) +
  geom_point()

ggplot(data, aes(x = kozak_region,
                 y = mean_ratio,
                 color = insert_sequence,
                 group = insert_sequence)) +
  geom_point()

ggplot(data, aes(x = kozak_region,
                 y = mean_ratio,
                 color = insert_sequence,
                 group = insert_sequence)) +
  geom_point() + 
  geom_point()

ggplot(data, aes(x = kozak_region,
                 y = mean_ratio,
                 group = insert_sequence)) +
  geom_point() + 
  geom_point() + 
  facet_grid(~insert_sequence)
